snippet.title: Factoring Trinomials (A quadratic Trinomial) by Trial and Error
snippet.description:
Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Factoring Trinomials (A quadratic Trinomial) by Trial and Error!
A brute force way to factor a trinomial, if it factors nicely.  Very, very tedious.  Unfortunately, also very, very common.
(Really, this is super fun.  I could do these all day.)
